Mortgage update! As we move into the holiday season here in 2023 I look around at the marketplace and I am so excited. Right now is an awesome time to purchase if you are in the position to do so. At this time you have less competition, and you have more of an opportunity to ask for seller concessions. Whether that be a reduced purchase price or an interest rate buy down. For every one percent that interest rates come down, an additional 5 million buyers now enter the marketplace. 
#
#
there will certainly be more competition if rates come down as discussed these past couple weeks. They’ve been coming down for the past six weeks consistently. Optimistic for the future to say the very least. Also, it is an election year, so take that into consideration. 
#
#
Thursday December mortgage thoughts 💭  let me know yours ! 🏡
